</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.slidedeck.com/social-network-wordpress/">How to create your own social network on WordPress?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.slidedeck.com">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Nishtha Dosaj";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8133:"<p>Has the thought of creating your own social network like Facebook or Twitter ever came to your mind?</p>\n<p>If not that big, maybe a small social network for friends or businesses. And if you think that would require a lot of coding or technical skills, then you are wrong. With <a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/">UserPro</a>, you can easily setup your own social network on WordPress. With UserPro&#8217;s addon &#8220;Social Wall&#8221;, you can add a wall on your site and help all the members interact with each other</p>\n<p>In this tutorial, we will guide you on how to create your own social network on WordPress.</p>\n<p><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Note : You need the latest version of UserPro (or minimum version 2.15) &amp; Social Wall Addon for UserPro in order to create your own social networking site.</span></strong></p>\n<h2>Creating a social network on WordPress</h2>\n<h4>STEP ONE :- Installation</h4>\n<p>You will first need to install and activate the <strong>UserPro Plugin </strong>and it&#8217;s<strong> Social Wall Addon</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19114 size-full" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/socialwall-activate.png?x36543" alt="UserPro social wall addon" width="679" height="135" srcset="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/socialwall-activate.png 679w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/socialwall-activate-580x115.png 580w" sizes="(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px" /></a></p>\n<h4>STEP TWO :- Setup</h4>\n<p>Before you can begin, you’ll need to authenticate SocialWall License . Navigate to the SocialWall and select the Licensing tab. Here you need to enter your Envato Purchase code.</p>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19119 size-full" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/licensing.png?x36543" alt="WordPress social network - UserPro" width="583" height="234" srcset="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/licensing.png 583w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/licensing-580x233.png 580w" sizes="(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px" /></a></p>\n<h4>STEP THREE :- Create Social Wall</h4>\n<p>After activating the addon, you need to create a page/post &#8220;Social Wall&#8221; with the shortcode &#8211;</p>\n<p><code> [userpro template=socialwall] </code></p>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19113 size-large" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/social_wall_add_on_preview-580x556.png?x36543" alt="Social wall addon - UserPro" width="580" height="556" srcset="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/social_wall_add_on_preview-580x556.png 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/social_wall_add_on_preview.png 664w" sizes="(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px" /></a></p>\n<h4>STEP FOUR :- Settings</h4>\n<p>Now you need to make settings for your Social Wall. Go to <strong>WordPress Dashboard » UserPro » SocialWall</strong></p>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19115 size-full" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/socialwall.png?x36543" alt="Social wall - UserPro" width="282" height="265" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Userwall Tab</strong> &#8211; You can specify the <strong>Title</strong> for your Social Wall, <strong>Number of Posts</strong> (social feed like status updates &amp; comments) to be displayed on the page and make other settings as per your requirement.</p>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19116 size-full" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Display-settings.png?x36543" alt="Social wall - UserPro" width="548" height="597" srcset="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Display-settings.png 548w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Display-settings-532x580.png 532w" sizes="(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Report Tab </strong>&#8211; Allow users to report the post as objectionable.</p>\n<p><strong><span class="nodeLabelBox repTarget "><span class="nodeText editable "><span class=" ">Delete Social Wall Posts and Comments Tab</span></span></span></strong><span class="nodeLabelBox repTarget "><span class="nodeText editable "><span class=" "> &#8211;</span></span></span> Allow admin to bulk delete the posts and comments by filtering the post dates.</p>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19117 size-large" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/delete-wall-content-580x96.png?x36543" alt="Social wall settings - UserPro" width="580" height="96" srcset="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/delete-wall-content-580x96.png 580w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/delete-wall-content-768x127.png 768w, https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/delete-wall-content.png 1116w" sizes="(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Email Notification Tab </strong>&#8211; Admin can enable email notifications on below mentioned actions and also can change the email templates for the same.<strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Send email notification when user comments on a post</li>\n<li>Send email notification to author when user like/dislike on a post</li>\n<li>Send email notification to author when user like/dislike on a comment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href="http://userproplugin.com/userpro/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-19118 size-full" src="https://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/email-notification.png?x36543" alt="Social wall - UserPro" width="517" height="404" /></a></p>\n<p>Once you are done with all the settings, Click <strong>Save Settings</strong> button.</p>\n<p>And you are done!</p>\n<p>You can also have a look at the Youtube video &#8211;</p>\n<p><iframe width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qTNTuY1D-pw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>I hope this article helped you setting up your own social networking site using WordPress.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions/feedback. Please let us know in comments <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f642.png" alt="????" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<br/><br/><a href="http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg?x36543" alt="Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck" style="display:block;border:none;"/></a><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.slidedeck.com/social-network-wordpress/">How to create your own social network on WordPress?</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.slidedeck.com">Responsive WordPress Slider Plugin</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=GBSjj8U4BMg:YwZ6T8f-420:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=GBS